  dialogueHidesSubmit: 1
  lines:
  - "Sure! Oh, one second please. I seem to have misplaced my document\u2026 it\u2019ll
    be here somewhere\u2026."
  - "You: \u2026.. "
  - 'You: FACTION? '
  - "\u2026"
  - "Let\u2019s get through this quick."
  - "No hard evidence but I\u2019ve got information for you. "
  - "This virus they\u2019ve been using to shepherd and manipulate the population
    for their plan is doesn\u2019t exist."
  - "All the \u201Cinfected\u201D are government pawns disguised, acting to perpetuate
    the belief to all of you. "
  - "We\u2019ve done another investigation you can check out, regarding the same
    event as the previous investigation. Appears the events of that day were stage
    1 of their plan."
  - "We\u2019ll keep investigating and keep you up to date. Expect contact through
    messaging soon. "
